name: RAHH
description:
This NFT grants you exclusive access to the Viral Sauce Virtual Community and The Urban Blockchain Academy . 
  Our goal is to create customized NFT Avatars and wearables for the metaverse. 
We also provide alternative music solutions for Independent artist through blockchain technology. We wanna simplify the NFT onboarding process for beginners by playing games and making art relevant to the blockchain and crypto space. Every NFT purchase will go to helping the Urban Community learn why Cryptocurrency exist and how it’s used. Upon purchase your wallet address will be entered into a raffle to win $100 in tezos, 10 NFTs from our collection of your choice, and a custom NFT avatar with features of your choice and upgraded accessories. The drawing will be held on Christmas 12/25/2021. All proceeds will go to educating and ONBOARDING Urban Artist into the NFT/Crypto space and building a virtual space for the urban community. Thanks for supporting the Uban Blockchain Academy. Hope to see you in the Metaverse. Admin DYRT 
Artwork by Low Eyes
